{"tid":1968725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極力推薦］香港其實有好多本地好音樂。仲講Mr.Wally？","createTime":"2020-04-12T01:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T03:23:39.000Z","uid":343574,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa055e0460729df0cf6d4ba112f00e3365647ff","tid":1968725,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">介紹本地音樂之前<br />\n我想講翻幾句說話。</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本土優先</span></span>呢個概念唔知係你地心目中有幾重要，但樓主對此有十分嘅感慨：<br />\n<br />\n香港人之所以咁撚慘，就係因為好多時候資源比曬好多非本地人搶曬：例如學位、床位。<span style=\"color: violet;\">甚至乎連本地音樂都比人搶緊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">本土文化需要大家努力一齊捍衛</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該由外地人賦予文化新意義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好喇，入正題</span></span><br />\n下面小弟我推薦幾個本地音樂比大家欣賞下，可能你曾經聽過，又或者第一次聽，但希望你地都可以 以行動黎表示你地嘅支持，包括金錢贊助 又或者是最簡單嘅訂閱 Like同欣賞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">廢話唔多講，馬上介紹翻幾首</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">（排名不分先後）</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.Serrini</span></span><br />\n存活係香港本地創作入面好耐嘅一位本地歌手，小弟由初中已經開始聽佢啲歌，代表作有好多：《蘇菲亞的波霸珍珠奶茶》、《抑鬱十二月》等等，當然唔小得呢個代表作《油尖旺金毛玲》。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HJ8FREaoyVo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHJ8FREaoyVo&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=0a625269\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HJ8FREaoyVo</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2.林家謙</span></span><br />\n相信大家都有聽過《矛盾一生》、《心之科學》。無錯，佢就係呢兩首歌嘅作曲人。除左作曲之外，佢更加識得填詞同唱歌，亦都係一位新進嘅歌手。佢嘅歌喉十分特別，聽佢唱歌，聽下聽下莫名其妙會有一種抑鬱嘅感覺呢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sY_4K3b8YKU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsY_4K3b8YKU&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=f278d4c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sY_4K3b8YKU</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">3.周國賢</span></span><br />\n從《黃金入球》時代去到今日嘅《逃生門》，相信大家都並唔陌生，佢仲要因為微博上留左句「加油」比小粉紅批鬥，作為香港人點可以唔支持架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vqbR8deApPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvqbR8deApPU&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=76f801ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vqbR8deApPU</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">4.何韻詩Hocc</span></span><br />\n呢個就唔多講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw，你地睇左佢琴日live演唱會未<br />\n未睇仲唔快啲禁入去睇翻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WTTp5beMy9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWTTp5beMy9c&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=21592a38\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WTTp5beMy9c</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n其實仲有好多本地新進/舊歌手樓主未有提及，好似黃淑蔓、牙醫許等等。另外其實香港都仲有好多本地二次創作音樂，同埋本地社運音樂。<br />\n例如樓主就中意呢一首《自游》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W7AZdzXXJQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW7AZdzXXJQc&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=a456fe90\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W7AZdzXXJQc</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知你地最欣賞嘅本地歌手同本地歌曲係咩呢？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎討論：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">奶共豪、鳩叫GEM呢啲麻煩就唔好攞出黎講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0e4d5f70a6ffcd1402d5caa2cb6c0836938ac8c2","tid":1968725,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:40:40.000Z","msg":"希望大家能夠多些些支持本地音樂"},{"pid":"15a0a9ab82bca0c97164d0cde86c7727fab4b4d2","tid":1968725,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"其實本地音樂仲有好多好聽嘅歌架"},{"pid":"67bad043aee10f6e17f14d8721e4ffaa4f5ad6f3","tid":1968725,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:41:35.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal